column5: hey guys i had 2 guys cancel last min..i have room for 2 guys and 1 boat..if your intrested in comming and fishing for a week up at lake temagami send me a line..cost would be for the cabin 140.00 per person..
Have fun Rob! Hopefully a pair will step up and join you. Will be a great learning curve for them to feed off your years of fishing the lake...
I wish I could get the time off I would love to tackle that lake another time
I just wish I could get out of here.. and be there like I'm supposed to be by now!
wayne i feel for you. you and i know how beautiful temagami is, just being there makes all the diffrence in the world
An incredible opportunity, I wish I was able to take advantage of it.
going third week of june  to temagami , would love to o but cant get time off work good luck where are you staying
